    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="card-deck mb-3 text-center">
            <div class="offset-xl-1 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">📮 Voicemail and Fax to Email</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            Check your voicemail right from your email!
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Incoming faxes appear in your email inbox, and sending faxes is a snap from the portal!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="offset-xl-5 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">🗼 LTE Backup</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            Similar to a backup generator for your internet; detects when your internet is going down and is able to support your internet and phones until your ISP (Internet Service Provider) can get out and resolve the underlying issue.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="card-deck mb-3 text-center">
            <div class="offset-xl-1 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">🏪 Business Hours</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            With business hours configured the phone will ring normally during the workday, while after hours it will go straight to voicemail or destination of your choice.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="offset-xl-5 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">🗿 Reliability</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            Our phones require no on-site server, no maintenance and no costly technician to service or adjust how the system works. See how easy having a phone system can be!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="offset-xl-1 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">🧈 Ease of Operations</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            Our phones require only one or two cables to install and have a clear and easy to understand color screen. Dedicated keys for commonly used features like voicemail make them super easy to use!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="offset-xl-5 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">👓 Clarity</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            Are humming analog phones getting you down? Do calls sound muddy or low quality? Our phones support HD Voice for crystal clear calls, and audio is carried digitally right to your phone preventing many common voice quality issues.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="offset-xl-1 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">📼 Call Recording</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            Need to record a call? Need proof someone made a certain commitment? With our call recording feature, you can record incoming or outgoing calls or both!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
