                        <p>
                            A universal hold feature. Place someone on park and anyone else can pick up and respond.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="offset-xl-1 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">👨‍💼 Wired Headsets</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            Every deskphone supports wired headsets using the built in RJ9 port on the rear of the phone. Crisp, clear and dependable, wired headsets are an effective way to enable a hands free experience!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="offset-xl-5 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">📣 Intercom</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            With the press of a button instantly start a conversation with a particular person! When using intercom, their phone will answer immediately on speakerphone.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="card-deck mb-3 text-center">
            <div class="offset-xl-1 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">📟 Paging</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>
                            Communicate quickly or find someone in a large space with paging. This feature is built into our phones, we can also install dedicated paging speaker system.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
