                            No need to worry about staying connected with just Ethernet, stay mobile with our new WIFI phones!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="offset-xl-1 col-xl-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">☄️ Bluetooth</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
